 Program Logic Explanation – SavorSync Landing Page
 What is this code about?
This is the code for the landing page of a food delivery website called "SavorSync". It’s the first page users see when they visit the site. Its main job is to welcome users, show the brand logo/image, and have a button to take them to the login page. It’s built using HTML for structure, Tailwind CSS for styling and Java for functions.
________________________________________
Breakdown of Each Part
1. Head Section – Settings & Resources
html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SavorSync</title>
