    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/font-awesome@4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
•	<!DOCTYPE html> – Tells the browser this is an HTML5 document.
•	<html lang="en"> – Sets the language to English.
•	<meta charset="UTF-8"> – Makes sure all characters (letters, symbols) show correctly.
•	<meta name="viewport"...> – Makes the page look good on phones, tablets, and computers (responsive design).
•	<title> – Text shown on the browser tab.
•	Tailwind CSS link – Brings in the styling tool so we can use ready-made classes like bg-primary, rounded-lg, etc.
•	Font Awesome link – Allows us to use icons if we need them.
